{"type": "game", "name": "BattleBit Remastered", "steam_appid": 671860, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [2390150], "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reviews</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\u201d\u2026even in its current state, it\u2019s already one of the more captivating multiplayer shooters on Steam right now.\u201d <strong>IGN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\u201cBattleBit has echoes of what Eric Barone did with Stardew Valley: a small game that punches above its weight and wins people over with unexpected depth and quality.\u201d <strong>PC Gamer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\u201cIf you\u2019ve grown tired of extraction shooters and battle royale games and crave something more focused on gunplay, combat, and just having fun over grinding and seasons, I\u2019d recommend\u00a0<i>BattleBit Remastered</i>.\u201d <strong>Kotaku</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into chaotic, large-scale FPS battles with up to 254 players in <i>BattleBit Remastered</i>! Whether you're storming enemy positions with Assault or building critical defences as support, every role counts in this low-poly, adrenaline-pumping battleground. Squad up with open VOIP and level cities with fully destructible environments. Ready to experience the ultimate team-based warfare?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Primary features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructible Environments\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/8cff82274c102c808f6befc81329c82d.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/8cff82274c102c808f6befc81329c82d.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/8cff82274c102c808f6befc81329c82d.mp4?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tear down walls, collapse buildings, and reshape the battlefield with dynamic 'levolution' mechanics, where every action leaves a lasting impact on the world around you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully customizable weapons (WIP)\u00a0<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/ae6dfbe685917e39f5d2d4468f494a74.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/ae6dfbe685917e39f5d2d4468f494a74.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/ae6dfbe685917e39f5d2d4468f494a74.mp4?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Tailor your arsenal to your playstyle in <i>BattleBit Remastered</i>! Modify everything from scopes to grips or barrels to mags. Create the perfect weapon loadout to dominate every battleground.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >254 Player servers\u00a0<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/611117d20181595cbd811c9fa4f71487.poster.avif?t=1730393449\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/611117d20181595cbd811c9fa4f71487.webm?t=1730393449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671860/extras/61111